snippet.textDisplay: I'm so sorry that you have to live that way. There could be a medical explanation for it. Have bloodwork done for Babesia and other possible infections as well as hormone levels and a physical. Could also be a pituitary issue that has been overlooked. You deserve to feel better. Best wishes to you.
